menu "HSM Configuration"

    config HSM_MAX_DEPTH
        int "Maximum state hierarchy depth"
        default 8
        range 2 16
        help
            Maximum number of nested state levels supported.
            Higher values use more stack memory during transitions.

    config HSM_HISTORY
        bool "Enable state history feature"
        default y
        help
            Enable the state history mechanism which allows
            transitioning back to the previous state.
            Adds 4 bytes to HSM instance size.

endmenu
